evaluatorContext.idealResponse:
Design a multi-system orchestration for deal closure:

ORCHESTRATION: Deal Closure Workflow

---

WORKFLOW TRIGGER:
```json
{
  "trigger": "deal_closed_won",
  "source": "crm_webhook",
  "payload": {
    "deal_id": "deal-123",
    "customer": {
      "id": "cust-456",
      "name": "Acme Corp",
      "email": "contact@acme.com",
      "owner": "sarah@company.com"
    },
    "deal_value": 50000,
    "products": ["enterprise_plan"],
    "closed_at": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
  },
  "idempotency_key": "deal-123-closure-v1"
}
```

---

EXECUTION DAG:

```
    [1. Update CRM]
          |
    [2. Create Project] ──────┐
          |                    |
    [3. Schedule Meeting]      |
          |                    |
    [4. Send Welcome Email] <──┘
          |
       [Complete]
```

```json
{
  "execution_plan": {
    "steps": [
      {
        "id": "step_1",
        "name": "update_crm_status",
        "system": "salesforce",
        "depends_on": [],
        "can_run_parallel": false
      },
      {
        "id": "step_2",
        "name": "create_onboarding_project",
        "system": "asana",
        "depends_on": ["step_1"],
        "can_run_parallel": false
      },
      {
        "id": "step_3",
        "name": "schedule_kickoff_meeting",
        "system": "google_calendar",
        "depends_on": ["step_2"],
        "can_run_parallel": false
      },
      {
        "id": "step_4",
        "name": "send_welcome_email",
